sentences: Dylan Ryan (drummer) (born 1979 in Chicago, Illinois) is an American drummer and composer.
He is a founding member, along with Dave (The Diminisher) McDonnell, of Chicago's experimental rock trio, Michael Columbia.
The second Dylan Ryan / Sand recording, Circa, was released on Cuneiform Records in September 2014.
In 2017, Dylan Ryan formed a new band called Ether Feather and released an E.P. entitled Other Memory.
Dylan Ryan joined Man Man in 2018 under the moniker Jazz Diesel.
